data.title: Germany HND
data.meta_description: germany hnd - Free download as Text File (.txt), PDF File (.pdf) or read online for free. This document provides a list of waypoints for GPS abbreviations used in Germany. It includes over 100 entries with the waypoint name written out in German, an abbreviation for each entry, and the latitude and longitude coordinates for each location. The document notes that it provides this information as an unofficial service for reference purposes only.
